data.description: Rates are dropping, come get this gem before it's gone! Welcome to 5682 Levi Kramer in Lehman Estates! Fully updated, open floorplan, 1,948 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths total. Quartz kitchen counters, updated appliances, fixtures, and cabinets! See floorplans in pics for a detailed layout. New paint throughout. Vinyl flooring throughout. Laundry on main level. Huge rear deck and concrete patio, wood privacy fence, large rear yard. 2 car attached garage. Canal Winchester Schools. Convenient access to US33, I-70, I-270. Move-in ready! Vacant and easy to see.
